text: Dimitar Kamburski (, born 28 January 1966) is a Bulgarian rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Plovdiv
